  "detailed_description": "<h1>CHECK OUT OUR NEW GAME!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight for freedom of people in this dictature simulation!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use different skills to make the revolt gauge grow!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't get caught by submitting yourself to guards' abuse of authority!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Paint graffitis</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Images are the best propaganda. Paint graffitis on walls, make them bigger to gain more revolt points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/bc25f20732fe39c48eddccd755989146.poster.avif?t=1728848996\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/bc25f20732fe39c48eddccd755989146.webm?t=1728848996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destroy power figures </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The icons of the dictature keeps it in position of power. Use a hammer to break them and help people rise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/c2e441cf8b535ed724598f0fe25e1db3.poster.avif?t=1728848996\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/c2e441cf8b535ed724598f0fe25e1db3.webm?t=1728848996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stick April Fool on the back of state guards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humour is devastating against oppression. Stick April fool on the back of the guards to make them look ridiculous.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/dd8b3d8da5761fa8fab79fc1117db2bf.poster.avif?t=1728848996\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/dd8b3d8da5761fa8fab79fc1117db2bf.webm?t=1728848996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Without being caught and sent to jail!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abuse of authority, stupid orders, surveillance, are all dictature weapons to submit people. Be careful to stay discreet in order to prevent you from jail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/fe6c7d998ee083c5187f5c25d2c508c4.poster.avif?t=1728848996\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/fe6c7d998ee083c5187f5c25d2c508c4.webm?t=1728848996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Warning: all sounds in this game are buccal.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Credits:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Design & Programing by</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >@MatoLabu</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music & Sound by</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >@Tomavatars</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visuals by</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loeiz from Gem Rose Accent</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/d6b970aced6f53105bfcbcc2ee6caefa.poster.avif?t=1728848996\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/d6b970aced6f53105bfcbcc2ee6caefa.webm?t=1728848996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight for freedom of people in this dictature simulation!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use different skills to make the revolt gauge grow!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't get caught by submitting yourself to guards' abuse of authority!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Paint graffitis</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Images are the best propaganda. Paint graffitis on walls, make them bigger to gain more revolt points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/bc25f20732fe39c48eddccd755989146.poster.avif?t=1728848996\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/bc25f20732fe39c48eddccd755989146.webm?t=1728848996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destroy power figures </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The icons of the dictature keeps it in position of power. Use a hammer to break them and help people rise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/c2e441cf8b535ed724598f0fe25e1db3.poster.avif?t=1728848996\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/c2e441cf8b535ed724598f0fe25e1db3.webm?t=1728848996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stick April Fool on the back of state guards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humour is devastating against oppression. Stick April fool on the back of the guards to make them look ridiculous.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/dd8b3d8da5761fa8fab79fc1117db2bf.poster.avif?t=1728848996\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/dd8b3d8da5761fa8fab79fc1117db2bf.webm?t=1728848996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Without being caught and sent to jail!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Abuse of authority, stupid orders, surveillance, are all dictature weapons to submit people. Be careful to stay discreet in order to prevent you from jail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/fe6c7d998ee083c5187f5c25d2c508c4.poster.avif?t=1728848996\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/fe6c7d998ee083c5187f5c25d2c508c4.webm?t=1728848996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Warning: all sounds in this game are buccal.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Credits:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Design & Programing by</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >@MatoLabu</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music & Sound by</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >@Tomavatars</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visuals by</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loeiz from Gem Rose Accent</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/d6b970aced6f53105bfcbcc2ee6caefa.poster.avif?t=1728848996\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125870/extras/d6b970aced6f53105bfcbcc2ee6caefa.webm?t=1728848996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
